@@ -0,0 +1,70 @@
+# OpenTelemetry Compatibility Matrix
+
+Матрица совместимости платформенного стартера трассировки. Отвечает на вопрос: **какие версии Spring Boot / Java / OTel SDK / OTel Agent считаются поддерживаемыми**.
+
+Для traceability (требование → класс) см. [traceability.md](./traceability.md).
+
+Версии Gradle pins — единственный источник истины: [gradle.properties](../../gradle.properties). **Новые version properties не добавляем.**
+
+## Version pins (Gradle)
+
+| Property | Значение (v0.1.0) | Назначение |
+|----------|-------------------|------------|
+| `openTelemetryBomVersion` | 1.61.0 | OTel SDK/API BOM |
+| `openTelemetryInstrumentationBomVersion` | 2.27.0 | Instrumentation BOM; **source of truth + expected Java Agent version** |
+| `openTelemetryInstrumentationAlphaVersion` | 2.27.0-alpha | Java Agent extension API |
+| `springBootVersion` | 3.5.5 | Spring Boot BOM |
+
+Gradle task `verifyOtelBomAlignment` проверяет:
+
+```
+openTelemetryInstrumentationAlphaVersion == openTelemetryInstrumentationBomVersion + "-alpha"
+```
+
+## Java Agent — derived operational contract
+
+```
+expectedJavaAgentVersion = openTelemetryInstrumentationBomVersion
+```
+
+Because OpenTelemetry Java Agent is supplied by runtime infrastructure and is not part of the Gradle dependency graph, this project does not define a separate Gradle property for it in v0.1.0. The supported Java Agent version is derived from `openTelemetryInstrumentationBomVersion`. Runtime packaging, Helm charts, Docker images and platform launchers must use the same major.minor.patch version.
+
+Gradle **не** проверяет runtime Agent. Синхронизация — ответственность DevOps (checklist при каждом апгрейде instrumentation BOM).
+
+## Supported (v0.1.0)
+
+- Java **21**
+- Spring Boot **3.5.x**
+- OTel SDK BOM **1.61.0**
+- OTel instrumentation BOM **2.27.0**
+- OTel Java Agent **2.27.0 exactly** (= `openTelemetryInstrumentationBomVersion`; **validated on 2.27.0**)
+
+## Patch-line compatibility
+
+По [OTel instrumentation VERSIONING](https://github.com/open-telemetry/opentelemetry-java-instrumentation/blob/main/VERSIONING.md): patch releases — bug-fix only; non-experimental configuration properties — breaking change policy. Линия **2.27.x совместима по OTel versioning contract**.
+
+Platform policy:
+
+- **Validated only on 2.27.0**
+- Production use других patch в линии 2.27.x требует smoke validation per platform policy (P1 e2e)
+
+Для board: не «supports all 2.27.x without testing», а «2.27.x compatible by OTel contract; platform validated on 2.27.0».
+
+## Not supported in v0.1.0
+
+- Java 11
+- Java 17 (если не прогоняется CI)
+- Spring Boot 2.7.x
+- Spring Boot 3.0–3.4 (если не тестируются)
+- Spring Boot 4
+
+## Правило обновления
+
+1. Правка **только существующих** properties в `gradle.properties` (ревью архитекторов + регрессионный прогон).
+2. `./gradlew verifyOtelBomAlignment` — compile-time alignment alpha/BOM.
+3. Checklist DevOps: синхронизировать Helm/Docker/platform Agent с новым `openTelemetryInstrumentationBomVersion`.
+4. P1 e2e smoke — required before production rollout (не блокирует architecture sign-off).
+
+## Связанные документы
+
+- [ADR-otel-direct-integration.md](../decisions/ADR-otel-direct-integration.md)

diff --git a/platform-tracing-test/src/main/java/space/br1440/platform/tracing/test/arch/OtelDirectIntegrationRules.java b/platform-tracing-test/src/main/java/space/br1440/platform/tracing/test/arch/OtelDirectIntegrationRules.java
